It’s disappointing when medium like Coke Studio doesn't give proper credit to the original creator of the song.
You Know the bengali portion "Amar kangkher koloshi" was written and composed by Akhil Thakur in Netrokona, Bangladesh. Though this song was very popular by Ukil Munshi also from Netrokona. you know people deserve to know the original creator behind the masterpiece song. why are you so reluctant to give artists proper credit?
